---

## Objective
The objective of this testing is to ensure that The Skill App allows users to manage appointments, calls, and client interactions smoothly, with accurate scheduling, notifications, and reliable mobile usability.

---

## Scope of Testing

### In Scope
- Mobile UI & usability testing
- Functional testing
- Appointment scheduling
- Call management features
- Notifications & reminders
- Navigation & screen transitions
- Error handling and validations

### Out of Scope
- Automation testing
- Performance and load testing
- Security testing
- Backend/API testing

---

## Test Approach
- Manual testing on mobile devices
- Scenario-based testing
- Exploratory testing simulating real user behavior,Download the app in my phone and tested all available features

---

## Test Deliverables
- Test Plan
- Test Scenarios
- Test Cases
- Bug & Observation Summary
- GitHub README documentation

---

## Entry Criteria
- App installed successfully
- Test build accessible
- User account available (if required)

---

## Exit Criteria
- All planned test cases executed
- All critical and major defects reported

---

## Tools Used
- Mobile Device (Android / iOS)
- Bug tracking via spreadsheet or direct reporting

